{"title":"Elite Training Desk puts laptop, tablet & phone in reach, all wires tucked out of the way","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/09/elite-training-desk-puts-laptop-tablet-phone-in-reach-all-wires-tucked-out-of-the-way/","date":1631199185000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085612/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_Eurobike-setup-800x686.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs%3Adevice%2Frscb28-1\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, Eurobike\" loading=\"eager\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-270994\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>The new adjustable Elite Training Desk provides a secure platform to keep electronics and training fuel within reach, while you focus on chasing personal bests in Watopia. Using solid materials and construction, the adaptable design should work with whatever you ride inside, while still managing to fold out of the way when not in use. Plus, with the best management of all the power cords needed to keep your gadgets running, the Elite Training Desk looks like the most well-thought-out method to tidy up your virtual riding setup…</p><h2>Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table</h2><div id=\"attachment_271007\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-271007\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, complete Elite indoor training setup\" width=\"1000\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-297x238.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-800x640.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-120x96.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-768x614.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-297x238.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-800x640.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-120x96.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085615/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_complete-Elite-setup-768x614.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-271007\">images c. Elite</p></div><p>When we saw Elite introduce their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/26/elite-rizer-simulates-climbing-descending-and-steering-for-realistic-trainer-workouts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">new Rizer</a> front wheel mount to better simulate climbing, descending &amp; steering for more realistic indoor workouts, it was clear they were going beyond elite-level trainers, and fully embracing interactivity. But while the images that came with the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/26/elite-rizer-simulates-climbing-descending-and-steering-for-realistic-trainer-workouts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rizer launch</a> included the basic Elite Posà stand that could hold your tablet, truly immersive training requires more gadgets these days.</p><p>Now, Elite’s premium smart trainers get just the extra gadget they were waiting for… a full-featured folding Training Desk that holds all of the interactive electronics you need for virtual riding, and does a great job of cable management, too!</p><h3>Tech Details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, phone &amp; laptop\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085618/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_loaded-768x480.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>The painted steel and oiled bamboo construction of the Training Desk repurposes the premium style of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/09/26/elite-tuo-brings-style-to-interactive-trainers-direto-x-gets-overhaul-adds-steering-control/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Elite Tuo smart trainer</a>, following along a similar design idea of being a quality piece of furniture that won’t look out of place in your house, even when you aren’t spinning your legs on a trainer.</p><p>From the top, you get a wide 70 x 40cm natural bamboo table surface with a smooth, easy-to-clean finish. A matching bamboo smartphone &amp; tablet support has two differently angled slots, so you can position your device perfectly. Then a couple of&nbsp; grippy anti-slip pads keep your laptop or smart devices from sliding around as you hammer on the pedals.<a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, stand\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085621/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folding-768x512.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>Designed to provide a secure base for all of your sensitive electronics during your indoor cycling workouts, the Elite Training Desk features a solid tubular steel frame construction, plus one wooden leg (like a pirate.) It uses a 3-point layout so it should remain stable even on irregular surfaces, and gets swivel caster wheels so you can reposition it slightly, even while in the saddle.</p><p>Table height is widely adjustable, from 75-120cm, so you should be able to dial in the perfect setup whether riding a trainer with the front wheel on or off. And a max load rating of 20kg (44lb) should be plenty for laptops, tablets, phones, water bottles, and training snacks.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, wires\" width=\"1100\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables.jpg 1100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-297x243.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-800x655.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-120x98.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-768x628.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables.jpg 1100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-297x243.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-800x655.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-120x98.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085624/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_hidden-cables-768x628.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>Besides stable construction, the Elite Training Desk’s standout feature is internal cable management. Sure, fully internal cable routing is the most popular buzzword in bikes these days, but keeping the power cables for all of you gadgets out of the way of spinning trainer parts is just as important.</p><p>Underneath the bamboo desktop, a wide &amp; deep compartment provides plenty of room to add your own power strip (not included from Elite). A cutout cover in the top hides the tangle of wires, with probably enough space to add chargers for your other bike-related gadgets as well.</p><p>Power cables go external along the support column, so it’s not fully wireless (kinda like new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/31/shimano-dura-ace-and-ultegra-deliver-fastest-shifting-ever-with-wireless-12-speed-groups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dura-Ace &amp; Ultegra Di2</a>), but Elite supplies Velcro straps for good external cable management, too.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, folded away\" width=\"1100\" height=\"600\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded.jpg 1100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-297x162.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-800x436.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-120x65.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-768x419.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded.jpg 1100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-297x162.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-800x436.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-120x65.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085627/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_folded-768x419.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>The simple 2-legged, 3-point layout folds down to a small footprint to push the Training Desk to the side when not in use (but the wooden leg snaps securely into place, so it shouldn’t collapse unexpectedly.) Or you can also quickly and easily break it down further for totally flat storage when not in use for a longer time.</p><h3>Elite Training Desk – Pricing &amp; availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085630/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_Eurobike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09085630/Elite-Training-Desk-multi-purpose-indoor-training-gadget-table_Eurobike.jpg\" alt=\"Elite Training Desk multi-purpose indoor training gadget table, Eurobike\" width=\"1350\" 